<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA39">
<l>ōttiṉ poruṇmuṭivu mittaṉaiyē yuttamaṉpē</l>
<l>rēttun tiṟamaṟimi ṉēḻaikā – ḷōttataṉai</l>
<l>vallīrē ṉaṉṟataṉai māṭṭīrēṉ mātavaṉpēr</l>
<l>colluvatē yōttiṉ curukku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To the extent that it fullfills the meaning of the recitation know, foolish people,</l>
<l>the way to praise the names of the Highest. If you don’t master that as a recitation,</l>
<l>if you don’t discern it well, [then] speaking the name of Mātavaṉ</l>
<l>is an abridgement of the recitation.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
